Perfect ✨ Deepika!

Let’s upgrade your royal bronze portfolio with animated shining particles (stars) in the background. This will make the whole theme more eye-catching and elegant.

We’ll use a canvas animation in JavaScript for the glowing particles.

---

Updated Code with Animated Particles

1. index.html

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

  <meta charset="UTF-8">

  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <title>Deepika's Portfolio</title>

  

  <!-- Google Font (Noelan / cursive style) -->

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- CSS Link -->

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

</head>

<body>

  <!-- Background Canvas for Particles -->

  <canvas id="particles"></canvas>

  <!-- Header -->

  <header>

    <h1 class="glow-text">Deepika Sri</h1>

    <p class="subtitle">Aspiring Developer | Designer | Creator</p>

  </header>

  <!-- Navigation -->
